'''二硼酸'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为B<sub>2</sub>(OH)<sub>4</sub>，它可用于制备有机硼酸。<ref>{{Cite encyclopedia|encyclopedia = [[Encyclopedia_of_Reagents_for_Organic_Synthesis|Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis]]|last1 = Little|first1 = Sarah|last2 = Trice|first2 = Jane|title = Tetrahydroxydiboron|year = 2001|publisher = [[John_Wiley_&_Sons|John Wiley & Sons]]|isbn = 9780470842898|doi = 10.1002/047084289x.rn01181}}</ref>

==合成==
[[三氯化硼|三氯化硼]]和[[乙醇|乙醇]]的反应最初于1931报道，反应生成二甲氧基氯化硼（B(OCH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>Cl），<ref>{{cite journal|last1 = Wiberg|first1 = Egon|last2 = Sütterlin|first2 = Walther|title = Zur Kenntnis einiger Verbindungen vom Typus BCl<sub>3−''n''</sub>(OR)<sub>''n''</sub>. (Über alkoxyl-substituierte Borchloride)|language = de|trans-title=Notes on some compounds of type BCl<sub>3−''n''</sub>(OR)<sub>''n''</sub>. (Via alkoxy-substituted boron chlorides)|journal = [[Z._anorg._allg._Chem.|Z. anorg. allg. Chem.]]|year = 1931|volume = 202|issue = 1|pages = 1–21|doi = 10.1002/zaac.19312020102}}</ref>后来，一种引入B-B键的新方法由此制备了四甲氧基二硼（B<sub>2</sub>(OCH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>4</sub>）：<ref name = Wiberg>{{cite journal|last1 = Wiberg|first1 = Egon|last2 = Ruschmann|first2 = Wilhelm|title = Über eine neue Borsäure (‚Unterborsäure’︁) der Formel H<sub>4</sub>B<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub> und ihre Ester|journal = [[Ber._Dtsch._Chem._Ges._A/B|Ber. Dtsch. Chem. Ges. A/B]]|year = 1937|volume = 70|issue = 6|pages = 1393–1402|doi = 10.1002/cber.19370700636|language = de|trans-title=On a new boric acid ('Sub-boric acid') of the formula H<sub>4</sub>B<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub> and its esters}}</ref>

::BCl<sub>3</sub>   <chem>->[\text{+ } \ce{CH3OH}][- \text{ } \ce{HCl}]</chem>   B(OCH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>Cl   <chem>->[\text{+ } \ce{Na}][- \text{ } \ce{NaCl}]</chem>   B<sub>2</sub>(OCH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>4</sub>   <chem>->[\text{+ } \ce{H2O}][- \text{ } \ce{CH3OH}]</chem>   B<sub>2</sub>(OH)<sub>4</sub>

==反应==
二硼酸在90 °C以上脱水，生成[[一氧化硼|一氧化硼]]，220 °C时完全失水。<ref>{{cite journal|last1 = Wartik|first1 = Thomas|last2 = Apple|first2 = Eugene F.|title = A New Modification of Boron Monoxide|journal = [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]|year = 1955|volume = 77|issue = 23|pages = 6400–6401|doi = 10.1021/ja01628a116}}</ref>

它是一种还原剂，在水中缓慢放出[[氢气|氢气]]。<ref name = Wiberg />

